<p><strong><span>推薦打手:</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>極巨化 巨金怪+ 極巨化噴火龍 (小招空氣斬)</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>@孔獻政 寶友分享</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>列陣兵打手比較</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>巨金怪vs噴火龍</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>意念頭鎚12vs空氣斬14，時間都是2T</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>Lv50</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>巨金怪輸出228.5*12=2742</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>噴火龍輸出199.9*14=2798.6</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>Lv20</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>162.4*12=1948.8</span></strong></p>
<p><strong><span>142.1*14=1976.8</span></strong></p>
